WEBVTT

01:29:37.691 --> 01:29:39.649
The wedding's been fixed,
and you're doing nothing about it?

01:29:39.733 --> 01:29:40.858
Just tell me what you want.

01:29:40.941 --> 01:29:42.774
Shouldn't we make a list
of relatives to invite?

01:29:42.774 --> 01:29:43.899
You do it.

01:29:43.941 --> 01:29:45.524
I don't really have
any relatives anyway.

01:29:45.649 --> 01:29:48.191
I've only got a few friends
and neighbours to invite.
